Generate a personalized career roadmap for transitioning from {{ current_role }} to {{ target_role }} at the {{ experience_level }} level in the {{ target_industry }} industry over an estimated {{ estimated_duration_months }} months.

Candidate Profile Context:
{{ context }}

Based on the candidate's profile, parsed skills, ATS score, missing skills (skill gap), GitHub projects, and interview history, construct a highly customized sequential career roadmap divided into distinct phases.

You must return a single JSON object with the following structure:
{
  "roadmap_title": "Actionable title for the roadmap",
  "target_role": "{{ target_role }}",
  "experience_level": "{{ experience_level }}",
  "estimated_duration_months": {{ estimated_duration_months }},
  "current_readiness_score": 60,
  "phases": [
    {
      "phase_number": 1,
      "title": "Phase Title",
      "objective": "Clear objective for this phase",
      "description": "Detailed description of what the user needs to learn and do in this phase",
      "estimated_duration_weeks": 4,
      "difficulty": "Beginner",
      "skills": ["SkillA", "SkillB"],
      "projects": ["Hands-on project description or title"],
      "certifications": ["Relevant certification"],
      "resources": ["Key learning resources or documentation URLs"],
      "completion_criteria": ["What defines completion of this phase"],
      "career_outcome": "What the candidate gains at the end of this phase"
    }
  ]
}

Ensure the response contains only the raw, valid JSON object matching this schema. Do not add markdown backticks, notes, or explanations.
